text: At least three warships of Japan have borne the name Nisshin: * a screw sloop launched in 1868 and scrapped in 1893 * a launched in 1903 and expended as a target in 1936 * a seaplane tender launched in 1939 and sunk in 1943 Category:Japanese Navy ship names Category:Imperial Japanese Navy ship names
title: Japanese ship Nisshin
